<main> 
    <div class="firstText">
       <h2>Private Day Tours from Reykjavík:</h2>
       <p>At Lilja Tours, we specialize in luxury private day tours in Iceland, offering discerning travelers tailor-made experiences that showcase the island’s breathtaking landscapes and cultural gems. Whether you're exploring the Golden Circle, the South Coast, or embarking on a custom Icelandic adventure, our exclusive tours are crafted to cater to your unique interests, ensuring a personalized and unforgettable journey.</p>
       <p>Would you be more interested in a <a href="/multiday/" title="see our multiday tours">personalized multiday tour</a>?</p>
    </div>

    <div class="wrapper">

    {allTours.filter((baba:any) => baba.data.filter==="norm").map((tour) => (

        <TourCards
tour = {tour}
>

</TourCards>
))}
</div>
<div class="firstText">
    <h2>Private Day Tours with Added Activities:</h2>
    <p>Enhance your Icelandic adventure with our private day tours that include unique experiences operated by trusted third-party providers. These tours combine the comfort of private transportation with exciting activities such as museums, lava tunnels, geothermal spa visits and more. The base price covers the vehicle, while an additional per-person fee applies for the selected activity upon booking.</p>
</div>

<div class="wrapper">

{allTours.filter((baba:any) => baba.data.filter==="extra").map((tour) => (

